{"sn45.34:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 45.34 ","sn45.34:0.2":"4. Patipattivagga ","sn45.34:0.3":"Parangamasutta ","sn45.34:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn45.34:1.2":"“Atthime, bhikkhave, dhamma bhavita bahulikata apara param gamanaya samvattanti. ","sn45.34:1.3":"Katame attha? ","sn45.34:1.4":"Seyyathidam—sammaditthi …pe… sammasamadhi. ","sn45.34:1.5":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, attha dhamma bhavita bahulikata apara param gamanaya samvattanti”ti. ","sn45.34:2.1":"Idamavoca bhagava. ","sn45.34:2.2":"Idam vatvana sugato athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","sn45.34:3.1":"“Appaka te manussesu, ","sn45.34:3.2":"ye jana paragamino; ","sn45.34:3.3":"Athayam itara paja, ","sn45.34:3.4":"tiramevanudhavati. ","sn45.34:4.1":"Ye ca kho sammadakkhate, ","sn45.34:4.2":"dhamme dhammanuvattino; ","sn45.34:4.3":"Te jana paramessanti, ","sn45.34:4.4":"maccudheyyam suduttaram. ","sn45.34:5.1":"Kanham dhammam vippahaya, ","sn45.34:5.2":"sukkam bhavetha pandito; ","sn45.34:5.3":"Oka anokamagamma, ","sn45.34:5.4":"viveke yattha duramam. ","sn45.34:6.1":"Tatrabhiratimiccheyya, ","sn45.34:6.2":"hitva kame akincano; ","sn45.34:6.3":"Pariyodapeyya attanam, ","sn45.34:6.4":"cittaklesehi pandito. ","sn45.34:7.1":"Yesam sambodhiyangesu, ","sn45.34:7.2":"samma cittam subhavitam; ","sn45.34:7.3":"Adanapatinissagge, ","sn45.34:7.4":"anupadaya ye rata; ","sn45.34:7.5":"Khinasava jutimanto, ","sn45.34:7.6":"te loke parinibbuta”ti. ","sn45.34:7.7":"Catuttham. "}